quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Iqeôb ed i medden uqeîîi nnsen, u nitni stehzan, ur d rzin"
  21,2,"Ur ten d ippas usmekti amaynut, s$uô Mass nnsen, mebla ma ppuraren, mara s sslen"
  21,3,"Ur d rzin wulawen nnsen. Ppemcawaôen wid idensen, s tuffra: \"d acu t wagi, siwa amdan am kunwi? Day a pvefôem ssêur, kunwi tepwalim"
  21,4,"Inna: \"Mass iw Iéôa timenna deg igenni, di tmurt. Neppa Issel, Issen"
  21,5,"Maca, nnan: \"d taffa n tirga. Xaîi! Isnulfa t id. Xaîi! Neppa d amedyaz. Aha san, ad a$ d iawi assekni, akken id ippuceggaâ i imezwura"
  21,6,"Ur tumin, uqbel nnsen, yal temdint Nesqucc, day ad amnen nitni"
  21,7,"Ur d Nuzen, uqbel ik, siwa irgazen, iwumi Nweêêa. Steqsit imawlan usmekti, ma ur teéôim"
  21,8,Ur ten Nerri d tifekkiwin ur ntepp lqut. Ur wekkôen
  21,9,"Sinna, Neîîef deg wayen i sen Nâahed, u Nsellek iten akked wid i £ ihwan. Nen$a imcumen"
  21,10,"Ih, Nessers awen ed Tazmamt, degs asmekti nnwen. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  21,11,"Acêal n temdinin idensen ay Neôéa! Nexleq, deffir sent, agdud nniven"
  21,12,"Mi êussen i lwaâôan nne£, atnan la regwlen, segs"
  21,13,"Ur regwlet ara, u$alet ar wayen is testasrem, ar ixxamen nnwen. Amar fellawen asteqsi"
  21,14,"Nnan: \"a yamxix nne$, nella, s tidep, d imednas"
  21,15,"Ur tfukk ti$ôi yagi nnsen, armi ten Nerra d aqecqac urhif"
  21,16,"Ur Nexliq ara, i wurar nne£, igenni, tamurt, akked wayen illan garasen"
  21,17,"Lemmer day Neb$i lhawiyya, yili Nebbwi p id, s $uône£, maday Naâna"
  21,18,"Xaîi! Nekkat tikerkas s tidep. Tneqq itent. Neqvent. A tawa$it nnwen, ilmend n wayen d teggarem"
  21,19,"IneS kra illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Wid illan $uôeS, ur sme$wôen ara iman nnsen, $ef uâabed iS. Ur âaggun"
  21,20,"Ppanzen iv akked wass, ur sêissifen"
  21,21,"Ne$ ddmen d, si tmurt, iôebbiten id ipparan ar ddunit"
  21,22,"Lemmer llin degsen iôebbiten, war Öebbi, war ccekk, ad fesden. Gedha s Öebbi, Mass n usgeld, seg wayen id ggaren"
  21,23,"Ur fellaS asteqsi $ef wayen Ixeddem. Nitni, fellasen asteqsi"
  21,24,"Ne$ day ddmen iôebbiten, war Neppa? Ini: \"Awit ed atebbet nnwen\". Ayagi d asmekti i wid illan yidi, d asmekti i wid illan, uqbel i. Maca, tegwti segsen, ur ssinen tidep. D$a zzin akin"
  21,25,"Ur d Nuzen amazan, uqbel ik, siwa ma Nweêêa yas ar: \"ur illi ôebbi siwa Nek, ihi âabdet iyI"
  21,26,"Nnan: \"Isâa Uênin aqcic\". Gedha s yiS! Xaîi! D imdanen imaâzuzen"
  21,27,"Ur S d zeggwiren deg wawal, xedmen s lameô iS"
  21,28,"Iéôa i illan zdat sen, akked wayen illan deffir sen. Ur ççafâan, siwa $ef win Iôuva. U nitni, si lxuf iS, pêadaren"